      "raw_text": "Another surprise was\nsprung by the new admins\ntration today.\n\n\nAS slant Corporation\nCounsel Rhodes this morn\ning caused the arrest Of e.\nPenhalleck, Northern Pacific\nengineer, for blocking the\ncrossing near Seventh av.\nConductor Lee Fisher will\nalso be arrested as soon as\nhe can be located. Penhal-\nleck deposited a $25 bond.\n\n\nDid you ever hear of any\nthing like that before? The\nrailroads have apparently\noverlooked the city election\nresults. They had come to\nregard street crossings as\nprivate property.\n\n\na a a = = = n a n - u u u u"
